I used this for the avocado photos to bring them down to roughly 500kb.
reduce image sizes to 50% of their original size and set the quality to 85%. Use the following command in the terminal while in the directory containing the images
magick mogrify -resize 50% -quality 85 -auto-orient -strip *.jpeg   
